  "decision_conditions": [
    "Condition : 1 - The development shall be carried out in accordance with the reports, specifications and drawings detailed PP-13665547v1, 03_2755_03B, 02_2755_02C.\r\nReason: To ensure a satisfactory standard of development and to allow the local planning authority to review any potential changes to the scheme. \r\n",
